cs.CV, cs.GR, cs.MM, cs.IR, cs.LG. 

The paper deals with image processing and computer vision, specifically illuminant estimation. Therefore, cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition) is the most likely sub-category. The paper also involves image analysis and graphics, which could fall under cs.GR (Graphics) and cs.MM (Multimedia). The use of algorithms and performance evaluation suggests cs.IR (Information Retrieval) and cs.LG (Machine Learning) as possible sub-categories as well.
